data.description: Room to spread out in this 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home with a welcoming front porch and huge deck in the backyard, great spaces for enjoying the outdoors. Convenient location featuring 2 Bedrooms with connecting bath and laundry on the main floor and 2 generous bedrooms with a full bath on the second floor. Look for the full wall of storage and a cedar closet in the upstairs hallway. Spacious living and dining rooms with beautiful natural wood. The main floor family room has a cozy feel with its knotty pine paneling and French doors. Plenty of options in the basement with an additional kitchen, laundry area, and 3/4 bath.  New HVAC and roof in the past five years and new windows on the main floor in the past ten years. Huge oversized 2 car garage.
